# Netlify redirects for Single Page Application

# Redirect all routes to index.html for client-side routing
/*    /index.html   200

# Optional: Redirect www to non-www (uncomment if needed)
# https://www.yourdomain.com/* https://yourdomain.com/:splat 301!

# Optional: Force HTTPS (uncomment if needed)
# http://yourdomain.com/* https://yourdomain.com/:splat 301!
